WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:01.900
Karl goes to primary school.

00:02.300 --> 00:05.300
He will finish school next year 
 after the 8th grade.

00:05.700 --> 00:09.000
The family does not have enough money for a 
 secondary school.

00:09.500 --> 00:13.900
Karl has to walk five kilometres to school
 because they live outside the town.

00:14.500 --> 00:19.100
Karl and his brothers share a bicycle, 
 which he is sometimes allowed to ride.

00:19.700 --> 00:25.700
After school, Karl delivers newspapers 
 to contribute to the family's living.
